HEADWORD: Alongside
<hw>A*long"side`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Along or by
the side; side by side with; -- often with <xex>of</xex>; <as>as, bring
the boat <ex>alongside</ex>; <ex>alongside</ex> of him;
<ex>alongside</ex> of the tree.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Alongst</ent>⟦br⟧
